ing: 1 (10 inch) angel food cake, cut into large cubes
des: "Store-bought angel food cake, toasted and rolled in sweet condensed milk, with a kiss of coconut for extra sweetness."
ins: Toast the angel food cake cubes over the coals of a campfire on toasting sticks until browned.  Dip the toasted cake into the condensed milk, and roll in coconut flakes.
